  color: #2c3e50;
}
```

### 3. ::selection

```css
/* Custom text selection */
::selection {
  background-color: #3498db;
  color: white;
}

/* Different selection for specific elements */
.important::selection {
  background-color: #e74c3c;
  color: white;
}

/* Firefox prefix */
::-moz-selection {
  background-color: #3498db;
  color: white;
}
```

### 4. Form Control Pseudo-elements

```css
/* Placeholder styling */
::placeholder {
  color: #95a5a6;
